Hi Guys! It’s me. I’m Michel & It’s small business Saturday ⭐️ Today is the day to shop small and support the main streets, the entrepreneurs, the hustlers working hard to live their dream ❤️ and defy the odds! 

I’m so grateful for all of you 🖤 keeping my career and dreams alive (nearly 15 years!) Your support, love & orders keeps me inspired and creative to do it everyday! I endlessly love what I do! 

I am so grateful for my team today — They keep this small business running (even during the craziest few years!) They are the BEST queens!

Remember to Shop Small! Especially Today ♥️

The days are long but the years are short and the balancing act is a real show but I wouldn’t change a single thing (except a little more help 🤣) I’m so proud they see how hard I work, being an entrepreneur and mom is as challenging as you would think it would be.❤️ Cheers to a successful 2024 both at home and at work! 2023 challenged me to my core but I learned so much and I love a good challenge, obvi 😊 and Thank YOU for following my story, supporting my stores, chatting with me and keeping me going 🍾🍾🍾
